{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/vim-plugins/","webpackCompilationHash":"419500739f58983f3fcf","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"写点东西","author":"hengstchon"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3ed6cb83-c9bd-562e-8981-606081184714","excerpt":"Vim Plugins 插件安装 插件安装方法，用 ，以  为例。 添加至 ： 然后执行：  是  简写， 表示当前文件。 mhinz/vim-startify GitHub repo 在 Vim 或打开界面显示最近使用的文件，无需设置，开箱即用。 skielbasa/vim-material-monokai…","html":"<h1>Vim Plugins</h1>\n<h2>插件安装</h2>\n<p>插件安装方法，用 <code class=\"language-text\">VimPlug</code>，以 <code class=\"language-text\">mhinz/vim-startify</code> 为例。</p>\n<p>添加至 <code class=\"language-text\">.vimrc</code>：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">plug <span class=\"token string\">'mhinz/vim-startify'</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>然后执行：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">:so %\n:PlugInstall</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">so</code> 是 <code class=\"language-text\">source</code> 简写，<code class=\"language-text\">%</code> 表示当前文件。</p>\n<h3>mhinz/vim-startify</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/mhinz/vim-startify\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>在 Vim 或打开界面显示最近使用的文件，无需设置，开箱即用。</p>\n<h3>skielbasa/vim-material-monokai</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/skielbasa/vim-material-monokai\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>之前一直在用的主题，综合了 monokai 和 material 的特点，色彩鲜艳，对比度高，安装完成后，添加代码开启主题。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token keyword\">set</span> background<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>dark\n<span class=\"token keyword\">set</span> termguicolors\ncolorscheme material-monokai</code></pre></div>\n<h3>lifepillar/vim-solarized8</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/lifepillar/vim-solarized8\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>现在在用的主题，更沉稳护眼。</p>\n<h3>itchyny/lightline.vim</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/itchyny/lightline.vim\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>状态栏插件，简洁美观。配合<code class=\"language-text\">solarized8</code> 主题使用时可调整相应配色：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> g:lightline <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token string\">'colorscheme'</span><span class=\"token keyword\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'solarized'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>scrooloose/nerdtree</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/scrooloose/nerdtree\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>系统文件浏览插件，更改开关快捷键为<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;C-n&gt;</code>：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">noremap <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>C-n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> :NERDTreeToggle<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>CR<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>快捷键：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th>File node mappings</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">o</code> / <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;CR&gt;</code></td>\n<td>open in prev window</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">go</code></td>\n<td>preview</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">i</code></td>\n<td>open split</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">s</code></td>\n<td>open vsplit</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th>Directory node mappings</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">o</code> / <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;CR&gt;</code></td>\n<td>open &#x26; close node</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">x</code></td>\n<td>close parent of node</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">X</code></td>\n<td>close all child nodes of current node recursively</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th>Bookmark table mappings</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">o</code> / <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;CR&gt;</code></td>\n<td>open bookmark</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">go</code></td>\n<td>preview file / find dir in tree</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">D</code></td>\n<td>delete bookmark</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th>Tree navigation mappings</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">P</code></td>\n<td>go to root</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">p</code></td>\n<td>go to parent</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;C-j&gt;</code></td>\n<td>go to next sibling</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;C-k&gt;</code></td>\n<td>go to prev sibling</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th>Filesystem mappings</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">C</code></td>\n<td>change tree root to the selected dir</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">u</code></td>\n<td>move tree root up a dir</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">r</code></td>\n<td>refresh cursor dir</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">R</code></td>\n<td>refresh current root</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">cd</code></td>\n<td>change the CWD to the selected dir</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th>Tree filtering mappings</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">I</code></td>\n<td>hidden files</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">B</code></td>\n<td>bookmarks</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>Yggdroot/LeaderF</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Yggdroot/LeaderF\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>文件搜索插件：The plugin is mainly used for locating files, buffers, mrus, ctags, gtags, etc in large project.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">.vimrc</code> 中添加：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> g:Lf_ShortcutB <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'&lt;leader>&lt;leader>b'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> g:Lf_DefaultMode <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'NameOnly'</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Default launch LeaderF: <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Leader&gt;f</code>.</p>\n<p>Once LeaderF is launched:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Command</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;C-r&gt;</code></td>\n<td>switch between fuzzy search mode and regex mode</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;C-f&gt;</code></td>\n<td>switch between full path search mode and name only search mode</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;C-j&gt;</code></td>\n<td>move the cursor downward</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;C-k&gt;</code></td>\n<td>move the cursor upward</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Up&gt;</code>/<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Down&gt;</code></td>\n<td>recall last/next history</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;C-x&gt;</code></td>\n<td>open in horizontal split</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;C-]&gt;</code></td>\n<td>open in vertical split</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;C-s&gt;</code></td>\n<td>select multiple files</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;!-- &lt;C-l&gt; --&gt;</code></td>\n<td>clear all selections</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>mattn/emmet-vim</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/mattn/emmet-vim\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>Settings in <code class=\"language-text\">.vimrc</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> g:user_emmet_leader_key <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">';'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> g:user_emmet_settings <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\\    <span class=\"token string\">'javascript'</span><span class=\"token keyword\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\\        <span class=\"token string\">'extends'</span><span class=\"token keyword\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'html'</span>,\n\\        <span class=\"token string\">'empty_element_suffix'</span><span class=\"token keyword\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">' />'</span>,\n\\        <span class=\"token string\">'snippets'</span><span class=\"token keyword\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\\            <span class=\"token string\">'re'</span><span class=\"token keyword\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"import React from \\\"react\\\"\"</span>,\n\\            <span class=\"token string\">'f1'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"(|) => {\\n\\t|\\n}\"</span>,\n\\            <span class=\"token string\">'f2'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"(|) => (\\n\\t|\\n)\"</span>,\n\\        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\\    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>,\n\\<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Now, the leader key is <code class=\"language-text\">,</code>.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Command</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">;,</code></td>\n<td>expand an abbreviation</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">;d</code></td>\n<td>select in tag(include tag)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">vit</code></td>\n<td>select in tag(exclude tag)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">;n</code></td>\n<td>go to the next edit point</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">;N</code></td>\n<td>go to the previous edit point</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">;i</code></td>\n<td>update an <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;img&gt;</code>’s size(only local img)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">;m</code></td>\n<td>merge lines</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">;k</code></td>\n<td>remove a tag</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">;j</code></td>\n<td>split/join tag</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">;a</code></td>\n<td>make an anchor from a url</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">lorem;;</code></td>\n<td>lorem ipsum(a paragraph)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">lorem{n};;</code></td>\n<td>{n} words</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Attribute operators:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Operator</th>\n<th>Attribute</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">.</code></td>\n<td>class</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">#</code></td>\n<td>id</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">[]</code></td>\n<td>custom attributes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">@</code></td>\n<td>number origin and direction</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Offitial tutorial:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">mvim ~/.vim/plugged/emmet-vim/TUTORIAL.mkd</code></pre></div>\n<h3>scrooloose/nerdcommenter</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/scrooloose/nerdcommenter\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>Setting in <code class=\"language-text\">.vimrc</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> g:NERDSpaceDelims <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> 1</code></pre></div>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Command</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">[count]&lt;leader&gt;cc</code></td>\n<td>comment</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">[count]&lt;leader&gt;cu</code></td>\n<td>uncomment</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">[count]&lt;leader&gt;c&lt;space&gt;</code></td>\n<td>toggle the comment state</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">[count]&lt;leader&gt;cy</code></td>\n<td>comment, but yank line(s) first</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>tpope/vim-surround</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/tpope/vim-surround\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>Surround.vim is all about “surroundings”: parentheses, brackets, quotes, XML tags, and more. The plugin provides mappings to easily delete, change and add such surroundings in pairs.</p>\n<p>Command structure:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>command<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>surround object<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>count<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>surround target<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>replacement<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Command</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>command</td>\n<td>y, d, c, v</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>surround object</td>\n<td>s, S</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>surround target</td>\n<td>(, )/b, [, ], {, }/b, &#x3C;, >, ”, ’, t, w, s, p</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">([{</code> with extra space.</p>\n<p>Tutorial with more detail: <a href=\"http://www.futurile.net/2016/03/19/vim-surround-plugin-tutorial/\">Vim surround plugin tutorial</a></p>\n<h3>jiangmiao/auto-pairs</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/jiangmiao/auto-pairs\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;C-v&gt;(</code>: insert paren ”(” without trigger the plugin.</p>\n<h3>luochen1990/rainbow</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/luochen1990/rainbow\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>Setting in <code class=\"language-text\">.vimrc</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> g:rainbow_active <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> 1</code></pre></div>\n<h3>bounceme/poppy.vim</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bounceme/poppy.vim\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>括号高亮插件，因为 vim-javascript 与 rainbow 在js文件中冲突，导致rainbow在js的函数中失效，可以用这个插件来稍微弥补一下。</p>\n<p>Setting in <code class=\"language-text\">.vimrc</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">au<span class=\"token operator\">!</span> cursormoved *.js call PoppyInit<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>iamcco/markdown-preview.nvim</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/iamcco/markdown-preview.nvim\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>Setting in <code class=\"language-text\">.vimrc</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">nmap <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>C-p<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Plug<span class=\"token operator\">></span>MarkdownPreview</code></pre></div>\n<h3>easymotion/vim-easymotion</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/easymotion/vim-easymotion\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>Settings in <code class=\"language-text\">.vimrc</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">map <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Leader<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Plug<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>easymotion-prefix<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nmap <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Leader<span class=\"token operator\">></span>h <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Plug<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>easymotion-linebackward<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nmap <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Leader<span class=\"token operator\">></span>l <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Plug<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>easymotion-lineforward<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>ntpeters/vim-better-whitespace</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/ntpeters/vim-better-whitespace\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>Setting:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> g:strip_whitespace_on_save<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>1</code></pre></div>\n<h3>prettier/vim-prettier</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/vim-prettier\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<p>Settings:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> g:prettier<span class=\"token comment\">#quickfix_enabled = 0</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> g:prettier<span class=\"token comment\">#config#bracket_spacing = 'true'</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>pangloss/vim-javascript</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/pangloss/vim-javascript\">GitHub repo</a></p>\n<h3>maxmellon/vim-jsx-pretty</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/maxmellon/vim-jsx-pretty\">GitHub repo</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Vim Plugins","date":"July 06, 2019"},"fields":{"slug":"/vim-plugins/"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/vim-plugins/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/re-introduction-JavaScript/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"A re-introduction to JavaScript"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/穷逼就别追星了/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"穷逼就别追星了"}}}}}